sequenceDiagram
    participant CO as CarOwner
    participant HO as HomeOwner
    participant SP as ServiceProvider
    participant CA as CAuth

    CO->>CA: Generate CSR and send signCSR request
    CA-->>CO: Return certificate (base64)

    HO->>CA: Generate CSR and send signCSR request
    CA-->>HO: Return certificate (base64)

    SP->>CA: Generate CSR and send signCSR request
    CA-->>SP: Return certificate (base64)

    Note over CO: Each stores keystore (end-entity cert and private key)
    Note over HO: Each stores keystore (end-entity cert and private key)
    Note over SP: Each stores keystore (end-entity cert and private key)
